column2: "Hey peon! You there peon! When I'm talking peon, you'd better listen!"
"Have I seen you before? I don't remember, so it doesn't matter."
"You haven't seen any enemies in this area? That's because I blew them all up! That's what I do!"
"But not just this area, to me and my Clarissa, there's nothing that can stand up to me! I blew everything up!"
"If I go too crazy I get tired, so I've just been blowing up things here and there."
"That person said the area where I can test my full strength is just beyond here."
"I'm really looking forward to it! I wonder just how much I can blow up without having to hold back!"
"Why would I not know my own strength? That's a stupid question peon, because I've never tried before."
"Have you tried using all of your strength? Everything? The full hundred percent of it?"
"If you've really done that, then how are you standing before me peon?"
"Conversation ends here. I feel like blowing stuff up again!"
